<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Elearning Activation  Account</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      margin : 0;
      padding : 0;
      min-width: 100%;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #333333;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }
    a{
        color: #000;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
    h1{
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight:700;
        line-height: 1.25;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
    }
    p{
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        margin-top: 0;
    }
    table td{
        vertical-align: top;
    }
    .email-wrapper{
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .email-header{
        background-color: #007bff;
        padding: 24px;
        color: white;
    }
    .email-body{
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 24px;
    }
    .email-footer{
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        padding: 24px;
    }
    .button{
        deisplay: inline-block;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 700;

        background-color: #007bff;
        color: white;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 5px;
        display: inline-block;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
   <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Account Activation</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Dear <%= user.name %>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for registering with our Learning Management System (LMS). To activate your account, please click the button below:</p>
            <h2><%=activationCode></h2>
            <p>please enter this code on the activation page within 5 minutes</p>
            <p>If you did not create an account, please ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>if you have any questions,please didn't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:support@securewavetechnologies.com">support@securewavetechnologies.com</a></p>
            <p>&copy; 2023 LMS. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
   </div> 
</body>
</html>